  "database_migration": "Additive migration 8 adds the independent Messages AI operational switch and a persistent per-conversation automatic-reply block. Existing SQLite data, encrypted keys, conversations, appointments, settings, custom knowledge, AI Control authorization and the 2,880-record automotive library are preserved.",
